precis:
Amendment to the MUNICIPAL GRANTS REGULATIONS, 1980 keeping within the
definition of "federal property" a building owned by Her Majesty and leased
to a designated airport authority, within the meaning of the Airport
Transfer (Miscellaneous Matters) Act.
